flowchart LR
    LAPI[Log-Level API\nEnvelope Provider Plugin Adapter]
    CME[Circulation Mechanism Engine\nPre-Bridge Write-Side Profile]
    BRIDGE[Bridge / Communication Context\nBridge-Facing Adapter]
    READ[Read-Side Circulation / Receiver Side\nDelayed release / retry / absorption]
    ADDONS[Addons / Final Receiver Surfaces\nDB / Thin C ABI / OTel / File Sink]

    LAPI -->|Prepared Envelope| CME
    CME -->|Passive Exposure / Dispatch Refs| BRIDGE
    BRIDGE --> READ
    READ --> ADDONS

    LAPI -. owns .-> LP[Parsing / Validation / Metadata / Timestamp / Assembly]
    CME -. owns .-> CP[Containers / Slots / Rounds / Waiting Lists / Refs]
    BRIDGE -. owns .-> BP[Protocol / Session / Channel]
    READ -. owns .-> RP[Receiver Delay / Retry / Failed Dispatch]
